=== The Gradient ===
--- gradient: pure function ---
double: (Int) -> Int
  -> double is Pure
     add 'with Pure' to unlock:
       memoization, parallelism, compile-time eval

--- gradient: effectful function ---
reader: () -> ?5 with IO
  -> reader does not access network
     add 'with !Network' to prove: sandboxed

--- gradient: already annotated ---
safe: (Int) -> Int

